4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior experience who aspire to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, with class sizes limited to 16 students. Participants will gain foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside practical skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The bootcamp helps students manage risks and navigate compliance standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. The program is available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop